OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,6,Frather cloudy with bright spells, the
OL,7,Fbest of the brightness expected over
OL,8,FOrkney. The chance of the odd spot of
OL,9,Frain across Shetland and winds
OL,10,Fmoderate, occasionally fresh from the
OL,11,Fsouthwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMainly dry with the best of
OL,14,Fthe brightness across Orkney this
OL,15,Fevening. Cloudier skies in Shetland,
OL,16,Fperhaps some patchy light rain.
OL,17,FModerate west or southwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
