OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAny early brightness will
OL,6,Ffade with outbreaks of rain developing
OL,7,Fduring the day, perhaps turning heavy
OL,8,Fand thundery later. Light to moderate
OL,9,Fsoutheast to southwest winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FEarly
OL,12,Frain on Friday, becoming dry and
OL,13,Fbright. Occasional rain or showers on
OL,14,FSaturday and Sunday. Variable winds,
OL,15,Ffresh at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
